                                     README
                                     ======

Description
-----------
  Keylogger for linux which uses the linux kernel notifier system.

Tested kernel versions
----------------------
  2.6.30   - works fine
  2.6.27-9 - key_callback will be never called

Todo
----
  - Write log in file or provide an interface over /proc or /dev.
  - Encrypt the log
  - Group the keys by user or tty (vc in key_event_state)
